      "message": "I started with grep because JGit already has `MessageRevFilter`, so this adds commit message filtering for `+log`, matching the `git log --grep` part of the issue.\n\nOne thing I would like to know is `grep` the right query parameter name for Gitiles?\n\nI mean the issue mentions two different “grep” concepts -\n\n```\ngit grep        # search file contents\ngit log --grep  # search commit messages\n```\n\nand I am suspecting later if we move towards a one general search box, then we might not know whether “grep” means *searching commit messages* or *file contents*? \n\nI would like to make sure the name does not conflict with the later search direction.",
